{"tid":191854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞典貨車恐襲兩男子被捕　其中一人是烏茲別克裔","createTime":"2017-04-08T07:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T07:40:13.000Z","uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47bbcadc3625855b19a7d3b4af82b3baa1bba5c0","tid":191854,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"瑞典首都斯德哥爾摩貨車撞向市中心百貨公司事件，警方拘捕兩人，相信其中一人是涉案貨車司機。<br />\n<br />\n警方早前發布一張身穿黑色上衣、綠色外套的疑犯相片，被捕的首名疑犯與相片中人的特徵吻合。當地傳媒指，疑犯是39歲烏茲別克裔人，是極端組織「伊斯蘭國」的支持者。<br />\n<br />\n事發於當地星期五下午，疑犯駕駛貨車撞向市中心人群，導致4死15傷，當中9人重傷，首相勒文指事件是恐怖襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1324099-20170408.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1324099-20170408.htm&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=0e226da9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1324099-20170408.htm&h=b141a715\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1324099-20170408.htm</a>"}]}